com.lowagie.rups.model
Class PdfFile

java.lang.Object
  com.lowagie.rups.model.PdfFile

public class PdfFile
extends Object

Wrapper for both iText's PdfReader (referring to a PDF file to read) and SUN's PDFFile (referring to the same PDF file to render).
